| Module | Translation Eval | Hints | Content Proc | Conversation | Gamification | Analytics |
|--------|-----------------|-------|--------------|--------------|--------------|-----------|
| **Practice** | ‚úÖ Core | ‚úÖ Core | ‚ö° Data | ‚ùå N/A | ‚úÖ Points | ‚úÖ Stats |
| **Reading** | ‚úÖ Sentences | ‚úÖ Words | ‚úÖ Core | ‚ùå N/A | ‚úÖ Reading | ‚úÖ Progress |
| **Memorize** | ‚ùå N/A | ‚ùå N/A | ‚úÖ Vocab | ‚ùå N/A | ‚úÖ Review | ‚úÖ Memory |
| **Conversation** | ‚úÖ Turns | ‚ùå N/A | ‚ö° Topics | ‚úÖ Core | ‚úÖ Chat | ‚úÖ Convo |
| **Progress** | ‚ùå N/A | ‚ùå N/A | ‚ùå N/A | ‚ùå N/A | ‚ö° Display | ‚úÖ Core |
