## üìä **Critical Path Dependencies**

### **Development Sequence**
```
Phase 1: Translation Evaluation (1) + Gamification (6)
    ‚Üì
Phase 2: Analytics (7) ‚Üí Hints (2) ‚Üí Content Upload (9) ‚Üí Reading Interface (8)
    ‚Üì
Phase 3: Content Processing (3) ‚Üí Flash Cards (10) ‚Üí Spaced Repetition (12)
    ‚Üì
Phase 4: Conversation Suite (4) ‚Üí Conversation UI (11) ‚Üí Topic Management (5)
```

### **Parallel Development Opportunities**
- **Modules 6, 7, 9, 8**: Can be developed simultaneously (No AI dependencies)
- **Modules 10, 11**: Can be developed in parallel once dependencies are met
- **AI Modules**: Must be sequential to build on shared infrastructure

